        <ul>
            <li>Facebook Page: <a class="btn-xs btn-success" href="https://facebook.com/dncuug">facebook.com/dncuug</a></li>
            <li>Facebook Group: <a class="btn-xs btn-success" href="https://facebook.com/groups/dncuug">facebook.com/groups/dncuug</a></li>
            <li>Telegram Channel: <a class="btn-xs btn-success" href="https://telegram.me/dncuug">telegram.me/dncuug</a></li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>